33
00:05:05,662 --> 00:05:06,991
We have a situation.

34
00:05:07,675 --> 00:05:10,685
Brian radioed in.
The Iraqi found the decoy village.

35
00:05:10,879 --> 00:05:12,501
Good. It's what we wanted.

36
00:05:12,657 --> 00:05:14,514
Brian followed him back to the shore.

37
00:05:14,886 --> 00:05:16,411
Ben, they have a sailboat.

38
00:05:16,841 --> 00:05:18,810
- How?
- I have no idea.

39
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:20,882
So they have a boat.

40
00:05:20,999 --> 00:05:22,719
Sailing in circles will keep them busy.

41
00:05:22,777 --> 00:05:23,969
They could find us.

42
00:05:29,017 --> 00:05:30,251
- Ben...
- I'm thinking.

43
00:05:33,131 --> 00:05:34,754
How quickly can you put together a team?

44
