See these rocks here? That's where you two come in.

72
00:10:44,767 --> 00:10:46,194
You're gonna chop 'em loose,

73
00:10:46,551 --> 00:10:48,174
and you're gonna haul 'em outta here.

74
00:10:48,291 --> 00:10:49,952
You expect me to work in this dress?

75
00:10:50,030 --> 00:10:51,222
It's up to you.

76
00:10:51,907 --> 00:10:53,471
